text: Federico Antonio Mariscal Abascal (24 September 1910 - 5 January 2002) was a Mexican diver. He competed at the 1928 Summer Olympics and the 1932 Summer Olympics. His brothers are Olympians Alonso Mariscal, Antonio Mariscal, and Diego Mariscal. ==Notes== ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1910 births Category:2002 deaths Category:Mexican male divers Category:Olympic divers of Mexico Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Divers at the 1932 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City
